The '''Dance Lords of the Bith''' was a [[Music/Legends|musical]] [[Band/Legends|group]] that was popular during the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]] they had just released a new recording and their music was played in the hottest clubs on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

==Behind the scenes==
This group is mentioned in a small delivery mission in ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'' called "Dance Lords Recordings."

